name: Apu Qon Rex
description:
A cyborg Dinosaur, or Qaraywa ("lizard" in Runa Simi, or the Quechua language), awaken and ready to rumble. The Dark Side is strong in this one.


Inspired by some of my original stories and characters from the time I was a 10 years old kid. And of course, by the Tyrannosaurus, the Allosaurus, Spinosaurus and science fiction stuff.

1080 X 1080 mp4 w/ sound

Original concept, sketch, drawing, digital illustration / painting, animation and sound edition by Zamahel
